e--stress-17492550240,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Starting thread AdService--stress-17492550241,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Creating thread AdService--stress-17492550241,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Starting thread AdService--stress-17492550243,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Running thread AdService--stress-17492550243,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,Creating thread AdService--stress-17492550241,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Running thread AdService--stress-17492550241,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Running thread AdService--stress-17492550240,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Creating thread AdService--stress-17492550243,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Running thread AdService--stress-17492550242,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Starting thread AdService--stress-17492550242,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : possible trigger for rule AdService--stress-1749255024 in class org.chaos_mesh.chaos_agent.TriggerThread,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,HelperManager.install for helper class org.chaos_mesh.byteman.helper.StressHelper,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,calling activated() for helper class org.chaos_mesh.byteman.helper.StressHelper,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,Starting thread AdService--stress-17492550240,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : possible trigger for rule AdService--stress-1749255024 in class org.chaos_mesh.chaos_agent.TriggerThread,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,Running thread AdService--stress-17492550243,出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["adservice-0", "adservice-2", "adservice-1"], "service_name": ["adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-07"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-07T00:10:23Z to 2025-06-07T00:29:23Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-07 00:10:23+00:00 to 2025-06-07 00:29:23+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "### Log数据分析结果\n\n**Stance**: NEUTRAL\n\n**Detected Log Keys**: \n- `AdService--stress`\n- `java.lang.Exception`\n- `InvocationTargetException`\n- `Agent failed to start`\n- `HelperManager.install`\n\n**Hypotheses**:\n\n1. **Component**: adservice\n   - **Reason**: 日志中多次出现 `Agent failed to start` 的错误，指出在 `adservice` 中代理未能成功启动。\n   - **Evidence**: `\"Agent failed to start!\"`, 出现次数 2\n\n2. **Component**: adservice\n   - **Reason**: 存在多次 `InvocationTargetException`，以及企图多次加载 Byteman agent，都指向可能存在的代码配置或重复加载错误。\n   - **Evidence**: `\"Exception in thread \\\"Attach Listener\\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\"`, `\"Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"`, 出现次数 2\n\n3. **Component**: adservice\n   - **Reason**: `AdService--stress` 和多次调用到 `stress` helper 类，可能表明这是由于性能压力测试导致的意外状况。\n   - **Evidence**: `\"AdService--stress-1749255024 execute()\"`, `\"HelperManager.install for helper class org.chaos_mesh.byteman.helper.StressHelper\"`, 出现多次\n\n从以上日志中提取的关键词和情境，表明 `adservice` 组件因加载问题或性能压力而可能导致故障。详细的调试信息如代理未能加载和多次调用异常提示对识别确切的故障原因是关键。", "metric_analysis_findings": "在分析期间，我发现以下显著异常指标和受影响实体：\n\n### 异常指标\n`detected_metric_keys` 包括以下 Top 3 的显著变化指标：\n1. `pod_cpu_usage`\n2. `client_error_ratio`\n3. `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`\n4. `node_cpu_usage_rate`\n5. `rrt_max`\n\n### 异常实体和原因\n根据已获取的数据，以下是主要的异常组件及其根原因：\n\n#### 1. Node 异常\n- **component**: \"aiops-k8s-08\"\n- **reason**: `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 和 `node_cpu_usage_rate` 异常升高，可能导致运行在该节点的所有 Pod 出现性能退化。\n- **evidence**: Node `aiops-k8s-08`上的 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 从正常的12GB下降到8.7GB，`node_cpu_usage_rate` 从34%升至42%。\n\n### 2. Pod 异常 (因 Node 异常导致)\n- **component**: \"redis-cart-0\"\n- **reason**: 由于其所在的节点 `aiops-k8s-08`资源使用率过高，导致 Pod `redis-cart-0`的 `pod_cpu_usage` 有轻微提高。\n- **evidence**: `redis-cart-0`的 `pod_cpu_usage` 在故障期间上升。\n\n### 3. Service 性能问题\n- **component**: \"cartservice\" (多个实例)\n- **reason**: `client_error_ratio`和`error_ratio`在服务 `cartservice` 上升，可能是由于其所在节点压力所致。\n- **evidence**: `cartservice-1` 和 `cartservice-2` 的 `client_error_ratio` 在故障期间显著提升。\n\n总体来看，故障根因可能是由于节点 `aiops-k8s-08`的资源紧张引发的，进而影响了运行在其上的多个 Pod 和 Service 的性能。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"node_cpu_usage_rate\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes and node_cpu_usage_rate exhaustion causing pod degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Node aiops-k8s-08's node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes dropped from 12GB to 8.7GB and node_cpu_usage_rate rose from 34% to 42%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Impact due to node aiops-k8s-08 resource high usage\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis-cart-0's pod_cpu_usage increased slightly during the fault\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio and error_ratio increase due to node pressure\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio for cartservice-1 and cartservice-2 significantly increased\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "成功获取了调用链的异常数据，我将开始分析这些数据以识别显著的异常和瓶颈。以下是初步的发现分析计划：\n\n### 异常调用链数据摘要：\n1. **显著延迟**\n   - 使用延迟倍数 (anomaly_avg_duration / normal_avg_duration) 鉴别。\n   - 已提取出主要的异常调用链（最多出现在Frontend、AdService 和 CartService 相关环节）。\n\n2. **异常状态数量**\n   - 重复陷入异常计数，这是关键指标之一。\n   - 主要在 `Ad GetAds` 以及 Redis-HMSET等环节累计。\n\n下一步将在 JSON 格式中返回分析初期结果。\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->AdService\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->CurrencyService\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency detected in 'AdService/GetAds' operations sourced by Frontend.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Latencies across related nodes: [30237ms, 38110ms, 31620ms] compared to normal averages [5431ms ~ 5557ms]. Occurred 38 times.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Checkoutservice observed abnormal delays in POST operations to CartService. Possible bottleneck.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Anomaly average duration peaked at 11.5s compared to 2.2s norm, detected with 'cartservice-2'.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Underlying Redis latencies significantly spiked, indicating a backend data persistence issue.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Average latencies for read/write: [35.2s, 12.3s], normal bounds before spike: 1.5s.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Fetching 'GetQuote' via ShippingService from Frontend showed delays exceeding normal.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Anomaly duration: [524ms ~ 862ms] versus [212ms]. Service was invoked multiple times.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Product fetch durations recorded were slightly errant/recurrent for downstream services.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"'/GetProduct' anomaly: jumped approximately 2X [9.2s]. Normal baselines remain ~7.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Requests into CurrencyService escalate affecting global availability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Requests tracked shows repetitive spikes pushing accumulated missed loads.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
